snippet.title: HUMANKIND - Together We Rule Expansion Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Unite HUMANKIND™ with the Together We Rule Expansion Pack! See the world in a new light and manage conflicts differently with new gameplay features focused on diplomacy and espionage.

Buy the base game here: https://humankind.game/

Follow HUMANKIND on social media!
Twitter: https://twitter.com/humankindgame   
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/humankindgame   
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/amplitudestudios   
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/humankindgame
